/* eslint-disable */
import React from "react";

export const MenuIcon = ({ fill, fillOpacity, ...props }) => (
  <svg
    width="26px"
    height="17px"
    viewBox="0 0 26 17"
    version="1.1"
    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
  >
    <g
      id="Symbols"
      stroke="none"
      strokeWidth="1"
      fill="none"
      fillRule="evenodd"
    >
      <g
        id="Menu"
        transform="translate(-48.000000, -7.000000)"
        fill={fill || "#fff"}
        fillOpacity={fillOpacity}
      >
        <g id="Group-16" transform="translate(48.000000, 7.000000)">
          <rect
            id="Rectangle"
            x="0"
            y="0"
            width="26"
            height="3"
            rx="0.5"
          ></rect>
          <rect
            id="Rectangle"
            x="0"
            y="7"
            width="26"
            height="3"
            rx="0.5"
          ></rect>
          <rect
            id="Rectangle"
            x="0"
            y="14"
            width="26"
            height="3"
            rx="0.5"
          ></rect>
        </g>
      </g>
    </g>
  </svg>
);
